m好正確。<br />\n<br />\nmodem有條細線連去個4x4既正方盒，講緊既應該係光纖機有條patch cord連去一個寫住fiber here 既socket，而再有條線去左牆身，咁去牆身個條就正正係條光纖。<br />\n<br />\n所以你套裝now係獨立運作，唔係分你屋企套上網既。<br />\n<br />\n而獨立又攪到你得返100既話呢 好大機會係個師傅拉線個陣整甩左你牆身個socket入面既青或棕線所以行唔到八芯。<br />\n<br />\n而最唔好彩既係佢直頭拉傷左你本身條線，但好少有咁既情況，因為傷線多線成條死唔會死一兩對。<br />\n<br />\n所以最簡單既方法係打開個牆身制望下粒骰仔有無啲線鬆左，有就搵一字批輕力啲跟色吉返入去，無既就真係要搵返你自己既上網公司幫你研究。<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999 <br />\n<br />\n有唔明可以私下問我"},{"pid":"45e163c01931db95500d70335fd91da2118541b1","tid":798244,"uid":13645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acd6fc089d07a00eb4ca65b27e756ac548edc6d8","tid":798244,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d4632716f773adb8c9923ffaa8cca97d0e92c8b","tid":798244,"uid":188521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"135587b23995b07d7e6469b6cddc04b6ea28a642","tid":798244,"uid":13645,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T07:30:56.000Z","msg":"我估係原本廳去房一條8芯lan 線<br />\n俾寬頻佬一開二變兩條4芯用<br />\n<br />\n4 芯最多行100mb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T09:06:51.000Z","msg":"真正答案 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T09:09:56.000Z","msg":"下 點會咁駁架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買個插頭 寬頻頭一開二 唔係更簡單咩？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T10:11:52.000Z","msg":"傻尻<br />\n你估萬能蘇一開二呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ddf487cd7807952e7a105dc3e8ff476f96f8f52","tid":798244,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45e163c01931db95500d70335fd91da2118541b1","tid":798244,"uid":13645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"acd6fc089d07a00eb4ca65b27e756ac548edc6d8","tid":798244,"uid":119330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d4632716f773adb8c9923ffaa8cca97d0e92c8b","tid":798244,"uid":188521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-29T09:06:51.000Z","msg":"